org.neuroph.contrib.imgrec.image.Image

Packages that use Image
org.neuroph.contrib.imgrec Provides classes for image recognition with neural networks. 
org.neuroph.contrib.imgrec.image Provides image abstraction to support the image recognition on J2SE and Android platform. 
org.neuroph.contrib.ocr Provides classes for Optical Character Recognition with neural networks.
